=head1 DESCRIPTION

Information about ownership of a managed node.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AccountId => Str

The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that owns the managed node.


=head2 OrganizationalUnitId => Str

The ID of the organization unit (OU) that the account is part of.


=head2 OrganizationalUnitPath => Str

The path for the organizational unit (OU) that owns the managed node.
The path for the OU is built using the IDs of the organization, root,
and all OUs in the path down to and including the OU. For example:

C<o-a1b2c3d4e5/r-f6g7h8i9j0example/ou-ghi0-awsccccc/ou-jkl0-awsddddd/>



